I understand that counseling may be a requirement in cases like mine, and I am open to participating in counseling as a means of personal growth and rehabilitation. I am willing to take any necessary steps to make amends for any harm caused and understand the importance of making restitution to the victim.

In conclusion, Your Honor, I acknowledge my guilt in this matter and plead for your leniency. I am deeply remorseful for my behavior and wholeheartedly commit to personal growth and change. I am grateful for your guidance and support as I work towards becoming a better member of society.

Thank you for your time and consideration.

